00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] dekadencijama i tako dalje.

1296
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:29,480
[SPEAKER_00] Oni ne svačaju da može postati

1297
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:31,320
[SPEAKER_00] civilizacija koja ima žrtvo.

1298
00:34:32,159 --> 00:34:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] Pa znate li mi moji dragi Hrvatske,

1299
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:36,579
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvati, dragi držaljane države Hrvatske,

1300
00:34:36,579 --> 00:34:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] štim smo mi pobjedili u domovinskom ratu.

1301
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] Štime?

1302
00:34:41,760 --> 00:34:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi smo imali oružje?

1303
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nispo.

1304
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi smo nametli bar ko ta isti zapad

1305
00:34:45,380 --> 00:34:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] na kojeg se sada mi zaklinjemo,

1306
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] a oružje nam dali Rusija.

1307
00:34:49,019 --> 00:34:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] Štim smo mi pobjedili?

1308
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] spremnosti Hrvatskog naroda na žrtvu.

1309
00:34:55,199 --> 00:34:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski branitelj je spreman,

1310
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] uzeo i branio se.

1311
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:00,719
[SPEAKER_00] E sada,

1312
00:35:00,719 --> 00:35:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Iranski narod je spreman na žrtvu.

1313
00:35:04,039 --> 00:35:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] A da bi to...

1314
00:35:05,239 --> 00:35:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] Vi hoćete mene.

1315
00:35:06,119 --> 00:35:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] 86 godina.

1316
00:35:07,599 --> 00:35:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je ovog.

1317
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:11,760
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo su se napravili medvjeđu uslugu,

1318
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:12,639
[SPEAKER_01] Amerikanci.

1319
00:35:12,639 --> 00:35:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su njega u šinskom,

1320
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] islam,

1321
00:35:16,219 --> 00:35:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ne samo to,

1322
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] nego i za sve druge

1323
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] muslimane napravili.

1324
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,780
[SPEAKER_00] On je za njih,

1325
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] za sve sada uzor.

1326
00:35:24,739 --> 00:35:28,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, zamislimo mi kršćani katolici.

1327
00:35:28,719 --> 00:35:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pa uopće ni to kršćani

1328
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji imaju euharistiju,

1329
00:35:31,739 --> 00:35:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] ne ove sekte.

1330
00:35:32,420 --> 00:35:33,639
[SPEAKER_00] Sekte su na ovom strani.

1331
00:35:33,639 --> 00:35:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] I to ćemo nešto reći.

1332
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:38,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo inicijaciju

1333
00:35:38,219 --> 00:35:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila u ovalnom uredu.

1334
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,239
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, to vas moram pitati.

1335
00:35:41,239 --> 00:35:43,079
[SPEAKER_00] To ćemo doći do toga

1336
00:35:43,079 --> 00:35:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] da ne zaboraviti,

1337
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] da u jednijavu prišli zaboravim.

1338
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:49,239
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zamislimo mi kršćani katolici

1339
00:35:49,239 --> 00:35:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] da nam neko ubije papu.

1340
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:51,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako.

1341
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je ista stvar.

1342
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je on vrhovni zapovjednik.

1343
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] On je papa u šinskom

1344
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] muslimanskom svijetu.

1345
00:35:58,719 --> 00:36:00,019
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujem da to je...

1346
00:36:00,019 --> 00:36:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerujem u jednog Boga

1347
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] koga nazivaju Allah.

1348
00:36:02,400 --> 00:36:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] Okej, sad mu je sin

1349
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] izabran za nasljednika.

1350
00:36:05,019 --> 00:36:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] E, a što je ta poruka?

1351
00:36:06,079 --> 00:36:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ga, gospod,

1352
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] nastavljamo istim.

1353
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] I onda narativno.

1354
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo istim putom.

1355
00:36:12,539 --> 00:36:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dok smo išljavamo u autu,

1356
00:36:13,900 --> 00:36:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] slušamo vijesti,

1357
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] onda govori ona spikerica,

1358
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, izabran je.

1359
00:36:17,679 --> 00:36:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] Jeli, sin od ajatoloha,

1360
00:36:19,579 --> 00:36:20,360
[SPEAKER_00] kam ne i je.

1361
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže,

1362
00:36:21,739 --> 00:36:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali on sada, kaže,

1363
00:36:23,559 --> 00:36:25,639
[SPEAKER_00] on je pod njegove zapovjedanje

1364
00:36:25,639 --> 00:36:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] i obogaćeni uran,

1365
00:36:27,199 --> 00:36:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] drugim riječima sugerira,

1366
00:36:28,460 --> 00:36:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] on će basiti

1367
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, nuklearnu bombu.

1368
00:36:30,900 --> 00:36:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, isti narativ

1369
00:36:31,980 --> 00:36:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] u hrvatskim medijima

1370
00:36:33,199 --> 00:36:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] i to ovaj govori.

1371
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,139
[SPEAKER_01] A hoće li?

1372
00:36:35,139 --> 00:36:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] Rekli ste da nemaju nuklearno.

1373
00:36:36,059 --> 00:36:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ako neko hoće

1374
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] uporabiti oružje,

1375
00:36:39,460 --> 00:36:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] to samo može biti

1376
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:42,280
[SPEAKER_00] Sjednjamečke države

1377
00:36:42,280 --> 00:36:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] ili Izrael.

1378
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] Niko drugi.

1379
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] Mislite nuklearno oružje?

1380
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] Taktičko nuklearno.

1381
00:36:45,599 --> 00:36:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Taktičko.

1382
00:36:46,059 --> 00:36:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Sad idemo na to područje.

1383
00:36:47,519 --> 00:36:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] Što je moguće u budućnost?

1384
00:36:49,099 --> 00:36:50,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zaboravajući onaj

1385
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] onojicijaciju

1386
00:36:51,199 --> 00:36:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] u uvalnom uredu.

1387
00:36:52,599 --> 00:36:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, o čemu se ovdje radi?

1388
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njima ne ide.

1389
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] Zato su u doktrinarnom smislu

1390
00:36:59,639 --> 00:37:01,280
[SPEAKER_00] Iranci primremili

1391
00:37:01,280 --> 00:37:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] šestu dimenziju rata.

1392
00:37:02,739 --> 00:37:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] A šesto dimenzije rata,

1393
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,320
[SPEAKER_00] autor moja malenkost.

1394
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] U knjizi

1395
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:09,159
[SPEAKER_00] suvreme umijeće ratavlja

1396
00:37:09,159 --> 00:37:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili vremena

1397
00:37:10,179 --> 00:37:11,780
[SPEAKER_00] jata i rojeva.

1398
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:12,900
[SPEAKER_01] Svi ga preporučujem

1399
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] da je pročitaju.

1400
00:37:13,619 --> 00:37:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da je progutaju u stvari.

1401
00:37:15,059 --> 00:37:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još kupiti.

1402
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:17,659
[SPEAKER_00] Izdavačka je kuća

1403
00:37:17,659 --> 00:37:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] ova iz Gorice,

1404
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] ova Venedikta,

1405
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] pa prema tome neka kupi.

1406
00:37:21,079 --> 00:37:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] Rata i jata i rojeva.

1407
00:37:23,179 --> 00:37:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jata su veće.

1408
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] Besplote letilice i rojevi

1409
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] su manje besplote.

1410
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:29,280
[SPEAKER_00] Evo tako i pojednostavljeno

1411
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] to reći.

1412
00:37:29,679 --> 00:37:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je

1413
00:37:30,059 --> 00:37:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] LDSR-aklije rezumije.

1414
00:37:32,119 --> 00:37:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] I šta su ovi napravili?

1415
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] Iranci, to viša tehnologija.

1416
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] Amerikanci su

1417
00:37:37,619 --> 00:37:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] rasporedili u ove vazalne države

1418
00:37:40,559 --> 00:37:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] sunitske

1419
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] vertikal kraljevine.

1420
00:37:45,300 --> 00:37:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, njihove vazalne

1421
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] u svojim bazama

1422
00:37:47,599 --> 00:37:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] i okolo njih

1423
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] sustav od sedam

1424
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:54,880
[SPEAKER_00] radara za daleko otkrivanje.

1425
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, radara za rano upozorenje se zove.

1426
00:37:58,460 --> 00:38:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] A to je više tisuća kilometara.

1427
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:04,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je sve da obranu Izrela

1428
00:38:04,699 --> 00:38:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] da bi oni mogli

1429
00:38:06,420 --> 00:38:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] prepremiti ovu željeznu kupolu

1430
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] vremena da bi mogli

1431
00:38:10,039 --> 00:38:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] zaustaviti let raketa,

1432
00:38:12,679 --> 00:38:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno ciljeva koji lete na Izrael

1433
00:38:15,539 --> 00:38:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] iz treće dimenzije rata.

1434
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] To je treća dimenzija.

1435
00:38:18,420 --> 00:38:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zato su važne.

1436
00:38:19,119 --> 00:38:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] Treća dimenzija rata.

1437
00:38:20,480 --> 00:38:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] I Izrael i Amerika

1438
00:38:23,159 --> 00:38:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] djeluju u trećom dimenziji rata,

1439
00:38:25,340 --> 00:38:28,179
[SPEAKER_00] dijelom u četvrtoj dimenziji rata,

1440
00:38:28,179 --> 00:38:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] dijelom u petoj.

1441
00:38:29,639 --> 00:38:30,980
[SPEAKER_00] Četvrta je realno vrijeme,

1442
00:38:30,980 --> 00:38:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] dakle odmah okrije luništi.

1443
00:38:33,059 --> 00:38:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] peta dimenzija sajberg i meneskog ratova,

1444
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,679
[SPEAKER_00] ali nemaju šesto dimenziju.

1445
00:38:36,679 --> 00:38:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] A šesta dimenzija su mreža.

1446
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:41,880
[SPEAKER_00] Mreža.

1447
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:42,800
[SPEAKER_01] Rat mreža.

1448
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Rat mreža.

1449
00:38:43,380 --> 00:38:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi su ovi napravili mrežu

1450
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] radara za rano otkrivanje.

1451
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] šta su Izraelice,

1452
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] Iranse pruništili?

1453
00:38:50,420 --> 00:38:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Te radare koji svaki košta,

1454
00:38:52,599 --> 00:38:54,820
[SPEAKER_00] cijenu oni uvijek nabiju

1455
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] do maksimalno da naprave nekakavu,

1456
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] da te zabljesne,

1457
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:01,159
[SPEAKER_00] milijardu i sto milijuna dolara.

1458
00:39:01,159 --> 00:39:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan taj radar košta.

1459
00:39:02,619 --> 00:39:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] I oni nemaju sada rano upozorenje.

1460
00:39:05,500 --> 00:39:06,900
[SPEAKER_00] Evo jučer je

1461
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:09,820
[SPEAKER_00] ministar obrane Izrela

1462
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] rekao i obavijestio

1463
00:39:11,679 --> 00:39:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] državljane države Izrela,

1464
00:39:13,619 --> 00:39:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno žitelje njihove,

1465
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] da oni se ne ljute

1466
00:39:17,260 --> 00:39:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] ako oni zakasne

1467
00:39:19,599 --> 00:39:22,360
[SPEAKER_00] sa davanje zračne uzbune,

1468
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] a da raketa već može pogoditi.

1469
00:39:23,980 --> 00:39:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jučer je to bilo.

1470
00:39:26,119 --> 00:39:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] Što to hoće reći?

1471
00:39:27,099 --> 00:39:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo upravo što govori.

1472
00:39:28,079 --> 00:39:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaju više tu

1473
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:31,360
[SPEAKER_00] dimenziju da oni

1474
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] otkriju se ovim vradama.

1475
00:39:32,699 --> 00:39:34,219
[SPEAKER_00] Da ti govori da tehnološki

1476
00:39:34,219 --> 00:39:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] pripremiš takvu operaciju.

1477
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da nešto što je

1478
00:39:37,039 --> 00:39:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] za Sjednjavečke države

1479
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] njeznu projekciju

1480
00:39:39,239 --> 00:39:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] vojnog milijući izuzetno bitno.

1481
00:39:40,639 --> 00:39:42,139
[SPEAKER_00] A što je to? Informacija.

1482
00:39:42,139 --> 00:39:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, a što ti radiš?

1483
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sa svojom mrežom,

1484
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno jatema,

1485
00:39:46,780 --> 00:39:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] bez plnuti letilica,

1486
00:39:48,199 --> 00:39:49,800
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno to su rojevi.

1487
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] I jata raketa,

1488
00:39:51,559 --> 00:39:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] uništiš čvorovište njihove mreže,

1489
00:39:54,920 --> 00:39:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja je komunikacija,

1490
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] ti si stekao enormu prednost

1491
00:39:58,300 --> 00:40:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] pred potivnikom.

1492
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] I treba će dobranu

1493
00:40:02,139 --> 00:40:04,019
[SPEAKER_00] sve njamečke države izrave

1494
00:40:04,019 --> 00:40:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] da to nadopunje.

1495
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se Americi,

1496
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] kao najjačoj vojnoj sili,

1497
00:40:07,659 --> 00:40:09,860
[SPEAKER_01] a Izrael nije ništa manje

1498
00:40:09,860 --> 00:40:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] kao loš osobito,

1499
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] ako ćemo u obaveštenom smislu

1500
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] da pače,

1501
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,659
