2311
01:01:33,579 --> 01:01:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] Je li sudjelao u drugom svjetskom ratu?

2312
01:01:36,340 --> 01:01:37,099
[SPEAKER_00] Nije.

2313
01:01:37,099 --> 01:01:38,719
[SPEAKER_00] Nije.

2314
01:01:38,719 --> 01:01:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nije u prvom drugom svjetskom ratu.

2315
