2342
01:02:41,360 --> 01:02:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] druga je stvar što je svako veljeposlanstvo,

2343
01:02:43,119 --> 01:02:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] špijunio.

2344
01:02:44,039 --> 01:02:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] I sad je otkrio toplu vodu

2345
01:02:50,139 --> 01:02:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] kako Iranci špijuniraju.

2346
01:02:52,000 --> 01:02:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] A to što oni špijuniraju,

2347
01:02:53,380 --> 01:02:54,280
[SPEAKER_00] što špijuniraju,

2348
01:02:54,280 --> 01:02:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] najveće izdvoji ove veljeposlanstvo

2349
01:02:56,400 --> 01:02:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] američke, to može biti.

2350
01:02:58,519 --> 01:03:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, oni mogu biti špijuni,

2351
01:03:00,019 --> 01:03:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] ali oni ne smiju biti špijuni.

2352
01:03:01,400 --> 01:03:03,820
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je ti kriteriji dvostavki u svemu.

2353
01:03:03,820 --> 01:03:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti ne možeš jednom suverenom državi

2354
01:03:06,099 --> 01:03:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] reći koga će ona primiti

2355
01:03:08,579 --> 01:03:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] i koga neće.

2356
01:03:09,340 --> 01:03:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome,

2357
01:03:11,340 --> 01:03:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] Iran je civilizacija,

2358
01:03:13,420 --> 01:03:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] čak i ima teorija onih naših

2359
01:03:15,199 --> 01:03:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] da smo mi iransko podrijetlani,

2360
01:03:16,579 --> 01:03:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] nismo, to je glupost

2361
01:03:17,539 --> 01:03:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] jednaka kao što je glupost

2362
01:03:19,579 --> 01:03:21,159
[SPEAKER_00] o nekakvim Slovenima.

2363
01:03:21,159 --> 01:03:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo, jer smo i potom cilirali.

2364
01:03:22,920 --> 01:03:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] A da je bilo mješanjstveno,

2365
01:03:24,000 --> 01:03:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] ništa uvijek je bilo i bit će ga.

2366
01:03:25,260 --> 01:03:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to sada.

2367
01:03:27,119 --> 01:03:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je Španjolska se izdvojila,

2368
01:03:29,539 --> 01:03:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda su krenuli sa svim

2369
01:03:31,199 --> 01:03:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] sredstvama njega,

2370
01:03:33,039 --> 01:03:34,900
[SPEAKER_00] ko što su sada i krenuli

2371
01:03:34,900 --> 01:03:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] na predsjednika Milanovića.

2372
01:03:36,539 --> 01:03:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednik Milanovića

2373
01:03:37,760 --> 01:03:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj vrijeme šutio u drugom odatu

2374
01:03:39,159 --> 01:03:40,320
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam čudio što on radi.

2375
01:03:40,320 --> 01:03:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je napravio dva odlična poteza.

2376
01:03:43,099 --> 01:03:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] Otišao je u Gruziju.

2377
01:03:46,420 --> 01:03:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo čak govorili prije odlaska

2378
01:03:48,039 --> 01:03:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] da bilo dobro da ode u Gruziju.

2379
01:03:49,440 --> 01:03:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad ste kod mene govorili.

2380
01:03:50,500 --> 01:03:51,619
[SPEAKER_01] Neko ode u Afriku,

2381
01:03:51,619 --> 01:03:52,639
[SPEAKER_01] neko ode u Pekiju,

2382
01:03:52,639 --> 01:03:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] neko ode u Rusiju.

2383
01:03:53,840 --> 01:03:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] Sada sam nabrojio što treba.

2384
01:03:55,659 --> 01:03:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] I on je otišao u Gruziju

2385
01:03:56,900 --> 01:03:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] i sad je izišao ovo,

2386
01:03:58,599 --> 01:04:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer ovo podložništvo

2387
01:04:00,380 --> 01:04:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] koje radi hrvatska vlada,

2388
01:04:02,280 --> 01:04:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] to je nešto zastrašujemo.

2389
01:04:03,420 --> 01:04:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] I premijer Plenković je malo

2390
01:04:05,400 --> 01:04:06,320
[SPEAKER_01] nakon toga rekao...

2391
01:04:06,320 --> 01:04:07,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pazi, nije ima izbora.

2392
01:04:07,420 --> 01:04:10,320
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer Milanović ga je stavio

2393
01:04:10,320 --> 01:04:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] presvršen čin.

2394
01:04:11,159 --> 01:04:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] On ima izbora.

2395
01:04:13,119 --> 01:04:13,860
[SPEAKER_00] Šta će on sada?

2396
01:04:13,860 --> 01:04:15,739
[SPEAKER_00] Da je on šutio tada,

2397
01:04:15,840 --> 01:04:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] on priznao da je u istinu vasal

2398
01:04:17,639 --> 01:04:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] izraelskog veliposlanstva.

2399
01:04:22,860 --> 01:04:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] I šutnja je odgovor.

2400
01:04:23,980 --> 01:04:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, jednako mora.

2401
01:04:24,880 --> 01:04:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je njegov opet.

2402
01:04:25,940 --> 01:04:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš ovako, možeš onako.

2403
01:04:27,840 --> 01:04:29,739
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to znači zapravo,

2404
01:04:29,739 --> 01:04:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] admirale, da po vašem mišljenju

2405
01:04:31,460 --> 01:04:32,699
[SPEAKER_01] mi kao Hrvatska

2406
01:04:32,699 --> 01:04:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] ne trebamo se petljati

2407
01:04:34,039 --> 01:04:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] ni u kakve ratove.

2408
01:04:35,059 --> 01:04:36,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ni zauzimati strane.

2409
01:04:36,920 --> 01:04:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] A učimo strategija.

2410
01:04:38,400 --> 01:04:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Davno uči.

2411
01:04:39,059 --> 01:04:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja samo citirali.

2412
01:04:39,980 --> 01:04:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] Svi mene naučili vremenom

2413
01:04:41,360 --> 01:04:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] za ovih 50 godina

2414
01:04:42,900 --> 01:04:44,480
[SPEAKER_00] koliko se bavim s njim i više.

2415
01:04:45,199 --> 01:04:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Prve, naučili smo je.

2416
01:04:46,039 --> 01:04:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, najbolji on je rat

2417
01:04:47,139 --> 01:04:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji ga nisim vodio.

2418
01:04:47,980 --> 01:04:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ima u doktrinama,

2419
01:04:49,519 --> 01:04:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji ona bitka

2420
01:04:50,460 --> 01:04:51,800
[SPEAKER_00] koju se dobio nisim vodio.

2421
01:04:51,800 --> 01:04:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] A mi Hrvati imamo primjer.

2422
01:04:54,699 --> 01:04:57,300
[SPEAKER_00] A to je povratak,

2423
01:04:57,300 --> 01:04:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] mirni povratak,

2424
01:04:58,119 --> 01:05:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] reintegracija Hrvatskog podunavlja.

2425
01:05:00,119 --> 01:05:01,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ratili se,

2426
01:05:01,239 --> 01:05:03,079
[SPEAKER_00] a nismo vodili ni bitku.

2427
01:05:03,079 --> 01:05:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jer nije pogunili

2428
01:05:04,239 --> 01:05:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] ni jedan Hrvatski vojnik,

2429
01:05:05,420 --> 01:05:06,300
[SPEAKER_00] niti protivnički,

2430
01:05:06,300 --> 01:05:07,300
[SPEAKER_00] ne preteljski vojnik.

2431
01:05:07,300 --> 01:05:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] To je najbolji rat.

2432
01:05:08,280 --> 01:05:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nijedan general

2433
01:05:10,119 --> 01:05:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] ni admiral ne žele voditi

2434
01:05:11,440 --> 01:05:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] nikakve ratove.

2435
01:05:12,300 --> 01:05:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] to svoji shlapljili političari,

2436
01:05:14,019 --> 01:05:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] oni koji služe

2437
01:05:15,340 --> 01:05:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] nekamu okultnu oligarhiji

2438
01:05:17,380 --> 01:05:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] koja svoji slizba pozadne

2439
01:05:19,039 --> 01:05:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] i njenih nje nema.

2440
01:05:20,059 --> 01:05:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] To je ovo.

2441
01:05:21,179 --> 01:05:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] To je moja poruka srbima.

2442
01:05:22,860 --> 01:05:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] Treći put.

2443
01:05:23,840 --> 01:05:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] Treći put.

2444
01:05:25,079 --> 01:05:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] daj osvijestite se.

2445
01:05:26,059 --> 01:05:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nisam ja slučajno

2446
01:05:27,639 --> 01:05:28,940
[SPEAKER_00] baš u vašoj nemisiji

2447
01:05:28,940 --> 01:05:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] ponudio savjest.

2448
01:05:30,480 --> 01:05:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je jedini način

2449
01:05:32,199 --> 01:05:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] da idemo mi zajedno

2450
01:05:33,059 --> 01:05:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] sačuvaj,

2451
01:05:33,559 --> 01:05:35,159
[SPEAKER_00] jer će nas gurnuti u rat ponovo.

2452
01:05:35,159 --> 01:05:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] A centar toga što radi

2453
01:05:37,960 --> 01:05:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] je u veleposlanstvo englesko

2454
01:05:40,619 --> 01:05:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] u Sarajevu.

2455
01:05:41,900 --> 01:05:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] Odatle to.

2456
01:05:42,639 --> 01:05:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da ome dinariku mute.

2457
01:05:44,619 --> 01:05:45,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja namjerim,

2458
01:05:45,519 --> 01:05:46,659
[SPEAKER_00] jer je to dinarika,

2459
01:05:46,659 --> 01:05:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] nikakav balkanski palot,

2460
01:05:47,820 --> 01:05:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] nego dinarik.

2461
01:05:48,500 --> 01:05:49,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dinara, dinarik.

2462
01:05:49,599 --> 01:05:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] Molim vas.

2463
01:05:50,099 --> 01:05:51,380
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto vas moram pitati.

2464
01:05:51,380 --> 01:05:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] Govorili ste,

2465
01:05:52,239 --> 01:05:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] rekli ste kako rat treba znati

2466
01:05:54,659 --> 01:05:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] i završiti.

2467
01:05:56,219 --> 01:05:58,900
[SPEAKER_01] Spomenuli ste da Rusija

2468
01:05:58,900 --> 01:06:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] to nije napravila u Ukrajini.

2469
01:06:00,500 --> 01:06:02,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad ovo je uvod.

2470
01:06:02,320 --> 01:06:02,860
[SPEAKER_01] Molim vas,

2471
01:06:02,860 --> 01:06:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] prije toga,

2472
01:06:03,659 --> 01:06:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] recite mi samo,

2473
01:06:05,260 --> 01:06:06,780
[SPEAKER_01] što mislite kako će se sada

2474
01:06:06,780 --> 01:06:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] ovo sve definitivno u Iranu odvijati?

2475
01:06:10,340 --> 01:06:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je teško reći.

2476
01:06:11,820 --> 01:06:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] Teško je?

2477
01:06:12,380 --> 01:06:12,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne.

2478
01:06:12,719 --> 01:06:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] To mislim,

2479
01:06:13,480 --> 01:06:14,860
[SPEAKER_00] opet, teško reći.

2480
01:06:14,860 --> 01:06:16,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ako se bavim strategijama,

2481
01:06:16,400 --> 01:06:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] mogu bar javno iznijeti.

2482
01:06:18,239 --> 01:06:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što razmišlja?

2483
01:06:19,099 --> 01:06:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] u kojem smjeru razmišlja.

2484
01:06:20,199 --> 01:06:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ne pretendiram bilo što da govorimo.

2485
01:06:22,059 --> 01:06:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] Opet smo rekli,

2486
01:06:23,739 --> 01:06:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] za njih sada slučajno upuca

2487
01:06:25,039 --> 01:06:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] ono te na treću.

2488
01:06:26,159 --> 01:06:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tamat,

2489
01:06:27,800 --> 01:06:28,820
[SPEAKER_01] trljenje,

2490
01:06:28,820 --> 01:06:29,679
[SPEAKER_00] tenkočutnost.

2491
01:06:29,679 --> 01:06:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Fog friction flexibility.

2492
01:06:33,099 --> 01:06:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

2493
01:06:33,420 --> 01:06:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] magla,

2494
01:06:33,820 --> 01:06:35,219
[SPEAKER_00] trljenje,

2495
01:06:35,219 --> 01:06:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] prilagodljivost.

2496
01:06:36,380 --> 01:06:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

2497
01:06:37,380 --> 01:06:38,840
[SPEAKER_00] to ovisi,

2498
01:06:38,840 --> 01:06:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] to ćemo pratiti.

2499
01:06:39,940 --> 01:06:40,719
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

2500
01:06:40,719 --> 01:06:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] Za sada,

2501
01:06:41,519 --> 01:06:42,860
[SPEAKER_00] imaš još nešto.

2502
01:06:42,860 --> 01:06:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su bili sigurni

2503
01:06:44,099 --> 01:06:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] prvi udaro bez glave,

2504
01:06:45,280 --> 01:06:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] ubiju ovoga

2505
01:06:46,800 --> 01:06:48,239
[SPEAKER_00] Hamneija.

2506
01:06:48,599 --> 01:06:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] Nasa će

2507
01:06:49,699 --> 01:06:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] promijenđa sa Hamneji,

2508
01:06:51,699 --> 01:06:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] oni će uzeti...

2509
01:06:52,559 --> 01:06:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] stiže po hlavi.

2510
01:06:53,300 --> 01:06:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] I gotovo.

2511
01:06:54,260 --> 01:06:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ili netko.

2512
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:55,639
[SPEAKER_00] Neko, nije bitno

2513
01:06:55,639 --> 01:06:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] ko je sa njima.

2514
01:06:56,579 --> 01:06:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] Samisli to,

2515
01:06:57,500 --> 01:06:58,059
[SPEAKER_00] koja je to

2516
01:06:58,059 --> 01:06:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] prepotentnost,

2517
01:06:59,559 --> 01:07:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] arugansija,

2518
01:07:00,360 --> 01:07:01,260
[SPEAKER_00] razum.

2519
01:07:01,260 --> 01:07:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću odrediti

2520
01:07:03,059 --> 01:07:04,300
[SPEAKER_00] ko će biti ajatolah.

2521
01:07:04,440 --> 01:07:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] zamisli on koji

2522
01:07:06,599 --> 01:07:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] uništene viruje,

2523
01:07:07,880 --> 01:07:09,860
[SPEAKER_00] a ima inicijaciju

2524
01:07:09,860 --> 01:07:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] od ovih.

2525
01:07:10,599 --> 01:07:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da će on

2526
01:07:12,300 --> 01:07:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] postaviti

2527
01:07:12,860 --> 01:07:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] vrhovnog zapovjednika,

2528
01:07:14,260 --> 01:07:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno vrhov

2529
01:07:15,559 --> 01:07:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] vijeskog voću,

2530
01:07:16,539 --> 01:07:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] pa sa tim

2531
01:07:17,739 --> 01:07:19,579
[SPEAKER_00] i glavnog zapovjednika,

2532
01:07:19,579 --> 01:07:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] predsjednika,

2533
01:07:20,800 --> 01:07:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] u Iran.

2534
01:07:23,199 --> 01:07:25,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je nešto

2535
01:07:25,780 --> 01:07:27,719
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatno.

2536
01:07:27,780 --> 01:07:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] nemoš vjerojatno

2537
01:07:28,400 --> 01:07:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] da tako možeš

2538
01:07:29,079 --> 01:07:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] sa nešto izreći.

2539
01:07:29,840 --> 01:07:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vidimo da možemo.

2540
01:07:30,840 --> 01:07:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] Zimu u takvom

2541
01:07:31,900 --> 01:07:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] blentavom svijetu.

2542
01:07:32,760 --> 01:07:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da tako budem jednostavno.

2543
01:07:34,159 --> 01:07:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se to je rekli?

2544
01:07:34,840 --> 01:07:35,820
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, blentavom.

2545
01:07:35,820 --> 01:07:37,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, sada vratimo se

2546
01:07:37,139 --> 01:07:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome.

2547
01:07:37,539 --> 01:07:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] Rusija,

2548
01:07:38,579 --> 01:07:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] o tom se puno govorili.

2549
01:07:40,920 --> 01:07:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] Rusiji,

2550
01:07:43,739 --> 01:07:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] evo što bi ja...

2551
01:07:47,860 --> 01:07:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, oni se još

2552
01:07:48,880 --> 01:07:50,099
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek mučaju u Ukrajini.

2553
