01:12:51,939 --> 01:12:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] ostalo nikako bije.

2767
01:12:52,880 --> 01:12:54,340
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nerazumnici jedni,

2768
01:12:54,340 --> 01:12:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] pa više, više te štete nanosite

2769
01:12:56,260 --> 01:12:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego Srbiju.

2770
01:12:58,460 --> 01:12:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jer krivo govorite.

2771
01:12:59,460 --> 01:13:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] Naime, mi smo ratovali

2772
01:13:01,819 --> 01:13:03,140
[SPEAKER_00] proti tri srpske vojske.

2773
01:13:03,140 --> 01:13:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ne jednu, nego tri.

2774
01:13:04,180 --> 01:13:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] I sve tri smo pobjedili.

2775
01:13:05,319 --> 01:13:06,399
[SPEAKER_00] Sve tri.

2776
01:13:06,399 --> 01:13:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] Jena je bila srpska vojska.

2777
01:13:10,399 --> 01:13:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] imala sve oružje,

2778
01:13:11,220 --> 01:13:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] mi ništa nismo imali.

2779
01:13:12,420 --> 01:13:14,479
[SPEAKER_00] A pa prijeli smo snagom žrtve.

2780
01:13:14,479 --> 01:13:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] Stragun opredjedljenja,

2781
01:13:16,380 --> 01:13:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] snagom umnog vojstva Tuđmana.

2782
01:13:18,539 --> 01:13:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nisu Rusi slučajno dali

2783
01:13:21,800 --> 01:13:24,979
[SPEAKER_00] odličje 1996. godine,

2784
01:13:24,979 --> 01:13:26,600
[SPEAKER_00] 1996. godine,

2785
01:13:26,600 --> 01:13:29,479
[SPEAKER_00] Tuđmanu orden maršal Žukov.

2786
01:13:29,479 --> 01:13:30,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je maršal Žukov?

2787
01:13:30,699 --> 01:13:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] Najveći vojskovača

2788
01:13:32,380 --> 01:13:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] drugog svjetskog rata,

2789
01:13:33,359 --> 01:13:35,279
[SPEAKER_00] što mu svi do jedne države

2790
01:13:35,279 --> 01:13:36,359
[SPEAKER_00] na zapadu priznaju

2791
01:13:36,359 --> 01:13:37,520
[SPEAKER_00] da je najveći vojskovačak.

2792
01:13:37,520 --> 01:13:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] A što je maršal Žukov?

2793
01:13:40,260 --> 01:13:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] učinio.

2794
01:13:41,260 --> 01:13:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] On je završio rat,

2795
01:13:43,319 --> 01:13:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] treba završiti rat.

2796
01:13:44,680 --> 01:13:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka budala može početi rat,

2797
01:13:46,800 --> 01:13:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] a samo veliki stratezi

2798
01:13:48,420 --> 01:13:49,399
[SPEAKER_00] znaju završiti rat.

2799
01:13:49,399 --> 01:13:51,640
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ona ima,

2800
01:13:51,640 --> 01:13:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali on nema iznaslu strategiju,

2801
01:13:53,420 --> 01:13:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] govorim pojmove

2802
01:13:54,220 --> 01:13:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] koje se javljaju u mediji.

2803
01:13:54,920 --> 01:13:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijem.

2804
01:13:55,539 --> 01:13:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] najveće umijeće vrhunac je

2805
01:13:58,699 --> 01:14:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] završiti rat

2806
01:14:00,260 --> 01:14:02,399
[SPEAKER_00] na način

2807
01:14:02,399 --> 01:14:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] da za 20-30 godina

2808
01:14:04,340 --> 01:14:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] ponovo ne vodiš rat.

2809
01:14:05,359 --> 01:14:07,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je umijeće rata.

2810
01:14:07,380 --> 01:14:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ej, sada Žukov,

2811
01:14:08,319 --> 01:14:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] što je napravio?

2812
01:14:10,100 --> 01:14:11,939
