2816
01:14:16,840 --> 01:14:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Digao zastavu.

2817
01:14:17,840 --> 01:14:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, zastavu digao.

2818
01:14:19,819 --> 01:14:20,979
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Tudžman

2819
01:14:20,979 --> 01:14:22,520
[SPEAKER_00] i zato su oni njemu dali.

2820
01:14:22,520 --> 01:14:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] Odliče Rusi.

2821
01:14:23,920 --> 01:14:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ti si,

2822
01:14:24,819 --> 01:14:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] presedniče Tudžman,

2823
01:14:26,840 --> 01:14:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] koji sam bio general,

2824
01:14:28,359 --> 01:14:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, ti si vrijedan

2825
01:14:30,579 --> 01:14:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] jednog Žukova.

2826
01:14:32,460 --> 01:14:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] E, moji Hrvati,

2827
01:14:33,720 --> 01:14:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] to van je domovinski rat.

2828
01:14:34,920 --> 01:14:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je znao završiti rat,

2829
01:14:37,340 --> 01:14:39,020
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne bi mogao završiti rat

2830
01:14:39,020 --> 01:14:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] bez oluje.

2831
01:14:40,760 --> 01:14:43,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pobjeda mora biti jasna

2832
01:14:43,140 --> 01:14:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] i čista.

2833
01:14:43,779 --> 01:14:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] Operacija oluja,

2834
01:14:46,239 --> 01:14:47,699
[SPEAKER_00] Srbi moji dragi.

2835
01:14:47,699 --> 01:14:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, dragi moji Srbi,

2836
01:14:48,880 --> 01:14:49,600
[SPEAKER_00] sad ću vam reći.

2837
01:14:50,579 --> 01:14:52,939
[SPEAKER_00] E, pa zato je ovdje svijednik

2838
01:14:52,939 --> 01:14:54,039
[SPEAKER_00] i to da spasimo

2839
01:14:54,039 --> 01:14:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] srpske živote

2840
01:14:55,039 --> 01:14:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] od srpske politike

2841
