[SPEAKER_00] jer ste htjeli,

2842
01:14:56,739 --> 01:14:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] vaša politika,

2843
01:14:57,779 --> 01:14:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] da mi pobijemo

2844
01:14:58,539 --> 01:15:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] 40 do 50 tisuća Srba,

2845
01:15:00,680 --> 01:15:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] da bi vi pokazali,

2846
01:15:01,640 --> 01:15:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] to su Englezu vas rekli,

2847
01:15:02,960 --> 01:15:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mi pokazali,

2848
01:15:04,140 --> 01:15:05,180
[SPEAKER_00] da bi vi pokazali

2849
01:15:05,180 --> 01:15:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] kako su mi genocidni narod.

2850
01:15:06,880 --> 01:15:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Eto ga.

2851
01:15:07,880 --> 01:15:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] I zato se operacija oluja

2852
01:15:10,039 --> 01:15:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] proučava na svim školama strategije.

2853
01:15:12,000 --> 01:15:14,560
[SPEAKER_00] I to je način kako se završava rat.

2854
01:15:14,560 --> 01:15:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je kako se treba završiti.

2855
01:15:17,220 --> 01:15:18,939
[SPEAKER_00] E tako treba završiti

2856
01:15:18,939 --> 01:15:20,000
