2857
01:15:20,000 --> 01:15:21,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ako to ove godine

2858
01:15:21,779 --> 01:15:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne napravi

2859
01:15:23,159 --> 01:15:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] rusko posto,

2860
01:15:26,720 --> 01:15:28,479
[SPEAKER_00] političko i vojnu,

2861
01:15:28,479 --> 01:15:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] onda

2862
01:15:29,960 --> 01:15:32,720
[SPEAKER_00] pitanje što će se sve dogoditi,

2863
01:15:32,720 --> 01:15:33,979
[SPEAKER_00] onda će dati uvjeta,

2864
01:15:33,979 --> 01:15:36,020
[SPEAKER_00] onda će oni se na zapadu

2865
