[SPEAKER_00] onda se oni stvarno

2870
01:15:44,100 --> 01:15:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] znaju ratovati dugo.

2871
01:15:45,640 --> 01:15:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ako iko zna dugo ratovati,

2872
01:15:46,920 --> 01:15:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] onda to znaju Rusi.

2873
01:15:47,819 --> 01:15:49,020
[SPEAKER_00] To se odmah razumijemo.

2874
01:15:49,020 --> 01:15:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni su na neki način

2875
