[SPEAKER_00] svoj spremni na žrtvu.

2876
01:15:51,760 --> 01:15:53,020
[SPEAKER_00] Na neki način uvijek.

2877
01:15:53,020 --> 01:15:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] E onda će oni,

2878
01:15:54,760 --> 01:15:55,560
[SPEAKER_00] ako to ne bude,

2879
01:15:55,560 --> 01:15:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] dati ovim lentavcima

2880
01:15:57,479 --> 01:15:58,880
[SPEAKER_00] u evropskim državama,

2881
01:15:58,880 --> 01:16:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] da ova okultna oligarhija

2882
01:16:00,619 --> 01:16:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] od Baltka do Jadrana

2883
01:16:01,739 --> 01:16:02,359
[SPEAKER_00] nas gurne

2884
01:16:02,359 --> 01:16:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] u drugu dionicu rata

2885
01:16:03,760 --> 01:16:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] proti Rusije.

2886
01:16:04,420 --> 01:16:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] Jer uprvo nisu Ukrajini.

2887
01:16:05,800 --> 01:16:07,220
[SPEAKER_01] Znači manjkavi su Rusi

2888
01:16:07,220 --> 01:16:08,680
[SPEAKER_01] po pitanju znanja

2889
01:16:08,680 --> 01:16:10,359
[SPEAKER_01] završetka rata.

2890
01:16:10,359 --> 01:16:11,520
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

2891
01:16:11,520 --> 01:16:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ih gledam.

2892
01:16:12,619 --> 01:16:13,439
[SPEAKER_00] Oni uopće,

2893
01:16:13,439 --> 01:16:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] početak napada na,

2894
01:16:15,039 --> 01:16:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno operacija,

2895
01:16:16,720 --> 01:16:17,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako oni zovu,

2896
01:16:17,260 --> 01:16:18,439
[SPEAKER_00] specijalno ili posredičko

2897
01:16:18,439 --> 01:16:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] rato u Ukrajini,

2898
01:16:19,079 --> 01:16:21,819
[SPEAKER_00] riječi i slovima

2899
01:16:21,819 --> 01:16:22,579
