2900
01:16:22,579 --> 01:16:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj i brojem,

2901
01:16:25,079 --> 01:16:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] imali su samo tri

2902
01:16:26,279 --> 01:16:27,220
[SPEAKER_00] besplote leteljice.

2903
01:16:27,220 --> 01:16:28,899
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

2904
01:16:28,899 --> 01:16:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tri besplote leteljice.

2905
01:16:31,739 --> 01:16:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] I naravno ti ne možeš,

2906
01:16:32,680 --> 01:16:34,060
[SPEAKER_00] a to je četvrta dimenzija rata.

2907
01:16:34,060 --> 01:16:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] A vidi sad sa besplode,

2908
01:16:36,100 --> 01:16:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ukrajini su su shvatili,

2909
01:16:37,880 --> 01:16:38,979
[SPEAKER_00] ono su na zapadu

2910
01:16:38,979 --> 01:16:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] i zato su uložili

2911
01:16:40,560 --> 01:16:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] najveće moguće sresta,

2912
01:16:42,119 --> 01:16:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer ono su najbrže dođeš,

2913
01:16:43,619 --> 01:16:44,800
[SPEAKER_00] najjeftinije

2914
01:16:44,800 --> 01:16:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] i digneš rat

2915
01:16:46,119 --> 01:16:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] iz druge, treće,

2916
01:16:47,539 --> 01:16:48,479
[SPEAKER_00] četvrte, pet,

2917
01:16:48,479 --> 01:16:49,699
[SPEAKER_00] u šestu dimenziju.

2918
01:16:49,699 --> 01:16:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijem.

2919
01:16:50,359 --> 01:16:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] Šesta dimenzija je moja dimenzija.

2920
01:16:52,260 --> 01:16:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam to,

2921
01:16:52,659 --> 01:16:53,699
[SPEAKER_00] zato sam i napisao

2922
01:16:53,699 --> 01:16:54,859
[SPEAKER_00] u Subraveno mješće ratovanje

2923
01:16:54,859 --> 01:16:55,439
[SPEAKER_00] i nazva to

2924
01:16:55,439 --> 01:16:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] šesta dimenzija rata.

2925
01:16:57,119 --> 01:16:58,699
[SPEAKER_00] Inače, sedma je rat zamračenja.

2926
01:16:58,699 --> 01:16:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] Peta je, rekli smo,

2927
01:16:59,659 --> 01:17:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] Kibernesko i ratovanje.

2928
01:17:05,819 --> 01:17:06,239
[SPEAKER_01] Sajber.

2929
01:17:06,239 --> 01:17:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] Sajber ratovanje,

2930
01:17:07,140 --> 01:17:08,420
[SPEAKER_00] Kibernesko i sajber ratovanje.

2931
01:17:08,420 --> 01:17:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] Četvrta je realno vrijeme,

2932
01:17:09,859 --> 01:17:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] ili besplotne leteljice.

2933
01:17:11,279 --> 01:17:12,619
[SPEAKER_00] Treća je zrakoplovstvo

2934
01:17:12,619 --> 01:17:13,640
[SPEAKER_00] i druga je pomorske,

2935
01:17:13,640 --> 01:17:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno kopljene snage.

2936
01:17:15,119 --> 01:17:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to su te dimenzije rata.

2937
01:17:17,420 --> 01:17:19,279
[SPEAKER_00] I sada je ona država,

2938
01:17:19,439 --> 01:17:20,760
[SPEAKER_00] koja može roti...

2939
01:17:20,760 --> 01:17:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, zašto Iran uspjeva

2940
01:17:23,180 --> 01:17:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] u tome to ponavljeno ponavljeno?

2941
01:17:24,359 --> 01:17:25,300
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer je rat digao

2942
01:17:25,300 --> 01:17:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] u šestu dimenziju.

2943
01:17:26,260 --> 01:17:29,600
[SPEAKER_00] A glavna projekcija moći

2944
01:17:29,600 --> 01:17:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] i Izraela,

2945
01:17:30,239 --> 01:17:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] i Svijemeške,

2946
01:17:31,579 --> 01:17:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] i s trećne dimenzije.

2947
01:17:32,600 --> 01:17:34,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, oni malo kaskaju,

2948
01:17:34,279 --> 01:17:35,020
[SPEAKER_01] malo, puno.

2949
01:17:35,020 --> 01:17:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] A kaskaju malo.

2950
01:17:36,260 --> 01:17:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ovi su

2951
01:17:37,079 --> 01:17:39,079
