[SPEAKER_00] mi ćemo odgovoriti

2955
01:17:41,859 --> 01:17:42,640
[SPEAKER_00] svojom mrežom.

2956
01:17:42,640 --> 01:17:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] To je ta mreža

2957
01:17:43,680 --> 01:17:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] sa jatama raketa

2958
01:17:47,279 --> 01:17:48,399
[SPEAKER_00] i rojevima bespilotnih.

2959
01:17:48,399 --> 01:17:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] U prijevodu napredniji su

2960
01:17:49,739 --> 01:17:50,439
[SPEAKER_01] u ratovanju.

2961
01:17:50,439 --> 01:17:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogušemo to reći

2962
01:17:51,779 --> 01:17:52,479
[SPEAKER_00] napredniji.

2963
01:17:52,479 --> 01:17:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, nije riješ

2964
01:17:53,579 --> 01:17:54,600
[SPEAKER_00] napredniji.

2965
01:17:54,600 --> 01:17:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, nego primjenju

2966
01:17:55,699 --> 01:17:56,479
[SPEAKER_00] adekvatnu

2967
01:17:56,479 --> 01:17:58,899
[SPEAKER_00] ili poželjnu doktrinu.

2968
01:17:58,899 --> 01:17:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, tako možda

2969
01:17:59,840 --> 01:18:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] ispravnije je bilo rečeno.

2970
01:18:01,380 --> 01:18:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] A kako bi taj rat,

2971
01:18:02,579 --> 01:18:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] recimo sada u Iranu,

2972
01:18:03,920 --> 01:18:05,859
[SPEAKER_01] mogao...

2973
01:18:05,859 --> 01:18:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje će tu biti

2974
01:18:06,500 --> 01:18:07,180
