01:23:17,380 --> 01:23:18,560
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje je tu racionalnost

3192
01:23:18,560 --> 01:23:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] i ostalog?

3193
01:23:19,359 --> 01:23:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne možeš,

3194
01:23:19,920 --> 01:23:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] to nije adekvatno oružje.

3195
01:23:21,079 --> 01:23:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ovo je,

3196
01:23:21,420 --> 01:23:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] rekli smo,

3197
01:23:21,880 --> 01:23:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] je treća demenzija,

3198
01:23:22,760 --> 01:23:23,380
[SPEAKER_00] ovo je šesta.

3199
01:23:23,380 --> 01:23:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako sam dobro shvatila,

3200
01:23:25,920 --> 01:23:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] postoji mogućnost,

3201
01:23:27,340 --> 01:23:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno još se nisu

3202
01:23:28,279 --> 01:23:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] na iransku stranu

3203
01:23:29,119 --> 01:23:31,060
[SPEAKER_01] uključili Kina i Rusija,

3204
01:23:31,060 --> 01:23:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] a ako se uključe,

3205
01:23:32,300 --> 01:23:33,479
[SPEAKER_01] procijenit ću sami

3206
01:23:33,479 --> 01:23:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad se uključe

3207
01:23:34,119 --> 01:23:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] i kako će se uključiti.

3208
01:23:35,239 --> 01:23:36,260
[SPEAKER_01] I na koji način,

3209
01:23:36,260 --> 01:23:37,319
[SPEAKER_01] sa kojim srestvima.

3210
01:23:37,319 --> 01:23:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] A onda što možemo očekirati?

3211
01:23:39,020 --> 01:23:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, onda možemo očekirati svašta.

3212
01:23:40,380 --> 01:23:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] Onda to je ta eskalacija,

3213
01:23:42,220 --> 01:23:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] zato je se naglasio,

3214
01:23:43,659 --> 01:23:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] posebno da ne ponavljamo se

3215
01:23:45,039 --> 01:23:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] mi u misli,

3216
01:23:45,619 --> 01:23:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] postošemo dosadne gledateljima,

3217
01:23:47,260 --> 01:23:49,439
[SPEAKER_00] taktisko nuklearno oružje.

3218
01:23:49,439 --> 01:23:52,060
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, postoji realna prijetna

3219
01:23:52,060 --> 01:23:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] od uporabe taktičkog nuklearnog oružja.

3220
01:23:54,579 --> 01:23:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka njegova uporaba,

3221
01:23:56,420 --> 01:23:58,020
[SPEAKER_00] sa bilo koje strane došla,

3222
01:23:58,020 --> 01:24:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] će voditi u eskalaciju

3223
01:24:00,420 --> 01:24:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] prema nuklearnom oružju.

3224
01:24:01,819 --> 01:24:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] U tome je cijela priča.

3225
01:24:04,060 --> 01:24:05,939
[SPEAKER_00] A kako ima glupih,

3226
01:24:05,939 --> 01:24:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] usijanih glava,

3227
01:24:07,399 --> 01:24:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] iz glupih odluka koje donose,

3228
01:24:09,319 --> 01:24:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] ništa nije isključen.

3229
01:24:10,640 --> 01:24:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kažem da hoće,

3230
01:24:11,640 --> 01:24:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte me krivo sati razumijeti.

3231
01:24:13,380 --> 01:24:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja govorim samo o opasnosti

3232
01:24:15,140 --> 01:24:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] koja je moguća.

3233
01:24:16,079 --> 01:24:18,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ali da ona manja,

3234
01:24:18,640 --> 01:24:21,399
[SPEAKER_00] Rusija mora što prije

3235
01:24:21,399 --> 01:24:25,340
[SPEAKER_00] završiti rat u Ukrajini.

3236
01:24:25,340 --> 01:24:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] Mora.

3237
01:24:26,279 --> 01:24:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

3238
01:24:27,239 --> 01:24:29,020
[SPEAKER_00] Mora da ostaje slobodne snage

3239
01:24:29,020 --> 01:24:29,739
[SPEAKER_00] i sve ostalo.

3240
01:24:29,739 --> 01:24:30,859
[SPEAKER_01] E.

3241
01:24:30,859 --> 01:24:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] A hoće li moći?

3242
01:24:32,159 --> 01:24:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] E, to ćemo tek vidjeti.

3243
01:24:33,300 --> 01:24:36,020
[SPEAKER_00] Imaju oni dovoljno isrestava,

3244
01:24:36,739 --> 01:24:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] imaju dovoljno...

3245
01:24:37,800 --> 01:24:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste primijetili kako je Ukrajina

3246
01:24:39,199 --> 01:24:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] sad malo po strani?

3247
01:24:40,220 --> 01:24:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] Hop, već su je zaboravili.

3248
01:24:41,500 --> 01:24:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, to je normalno.

3249
01:24:42,380 --> 01:24:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je sad stavilo po strani,

3250
01:24:43,739 --> 01:24:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] pa to je sve više iskoristiti.

3251
01:24:45,119 --> 01:24:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ima još nešto.

3252
01:24:46,680 --> 01:24:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jedini brod koji tamo je bio

3253
01:24:49,119 --> 01:24:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] u ovome

3254
01:24:49,819 --> 01:24:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] Arapskom,

3255
01:24:51,100 --> 01:24:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] ono je sad i u Arapskom moru,

3256
01:24:52,640 --> 01:24:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] bilo u ovome

3257
01:24:53,539 --> 01:24:55,520
[SPEAKER_00] Perskom zalju,

3258
01:24:55,520 --> 01:24:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] sad i u Arapskom moru,

3259
01:24:56,460 --> 01:24:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] je kineski brod,

3260
01:24:57,479 --> 01:24:58,739
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji i najsuremeniji

3261
01:24:58,739 --> 01:24:59,899
[SPEAKER_00] za elektronsko,

3262
01:24:59,899 --> 01:25:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] cyber,

3263
01:25:00,500 --> 01:25:03,420
[SPEAKER_00] kibernesko ratovanje,

3264
01:25:03,979 --> 01:25:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] cyber ratovanje, elektronsko izviđanje

3265
01:25:05,819 --> 01:25:06,659
[SPEAKER_00] i on prikupio sve.

3266
01:25:06,659 --> 01:25:08,159
[SPEAKER_00] Sve podatke.

3267
01:25:08,159 --> 01:25:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto je išao vano?

3268
01:25:10,079 --> 01:25:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ovi su dovukli razvorače,

3269
01:25:11,380 --> 01:25:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer on prati pomorske snage,

3270
01:25:12,720 --> 01:25:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] sada to je ključno.

3271
01:25:13,659 --> 01:25:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] Način kako djeluju.

3272
01:25:15,340 --> 01:25:17,020
[SPEAKER_00] Sve, sve, sve se obrađuje.

3273
01:25:17,020 --> 01:25:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] Umjetna inteligencija radi

3274
01:25:18,479 --> 01:25:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] maksimalnu snagu.

3275
01:25:20,439 --> 01:25:22,359
[SPEAKER_00] sve pročitava ovaj način

3276
01:25:22,359 --> 01:25:23,779
[SPEAKER_00] doktrine, algoritme što ima

3277
01:25:23,779 --> 01:25:26,060
[SPEAKER_00] za ovaj, kako se zove,

3278
01:25:26,060 --> 01:25:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] za Tajvan.

3279
01:25:28,140 --> 01:25:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ako se dobra

3280
01:25:30,680 --> 01:25:31,300
[SPEAKER_00] nas zaglavi,

3281
01:25:31,300 --> 01:25:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] ako ovako nastoje zaglavuće

3282
01:25:32,739 --> 01:25:34,399
[SPEAKER_00] i Amerika i Izrael,

3283
01:25:34,399 --> 01:25:36,180
[SPEAKER_00] tada Kini se stvaraju uvjeti

3284
01:25:36,180 --> 01:25:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] da ona uz relativno prihvatljivu cijenu

3285
01:25:39,239 --> 01:25:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] riješi Tajvan.

3286
01:25:40,619 --> 01:25:42,600
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ići će na njega.

3287
01:25:42,600 --> 01:25:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovo je tek početak priče

3288
01:25:45,180 --> 01:25:45,880
[SPEAKER_00] koja ide.

3289
01:25:45,880 --> 01:25:48,060
[SPEAKER_00] Prije će se,

3290
01:25:48,060 --> 01:25:49,939
[SPEAKER_00] daj Bože, da bude obrnuto.

3291
01:25:49,939 --> 01:25:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] Prije će se proširiti

3292
01:25:52,300 --> 01:25:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] ili naširiti,

3293
01:25:53,659 --> 01:25:55,020
[SPEAKER_00] nego što će se stati.

3294
01:25:55,020 --> 01:25:55,899
[SPEAKER_01] Nego smiriti.

3295
01:25:55,899 --> 01:25:57,819
[SPEAKER_00] Uvjeti za mene je

3296
01:25:57,819 --> 01:25:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] u idućim vremenima

3297
01:25:59,560 --> 01:26:00,340
[SPEAKER_00] dosta je bilo

3298
01:26:00,340 --> 01:26:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] četiri i pol godine rata.

3299
01:26:02,239 --> 01:26:03,939
[SPEAKER_00] Morate privesti operaciju,

3300
01:26:03,939 --> 01:26:05,479
[SPEAKER_00] morate izvesti oluju.

3301
01:26:05,479 --> 01:26:07,100
[SPEAKER_00] Bez oluje ne može ništa.

3302
01:26:07,100 --> 01:26:08,979
[SPEAKER_00] Gori na ruse,

3303
01:26:08,979 --> 01:26:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] mislim i ostaloga.

3304
01:26:10,000 --> 01:26:12,020
[SPEAKER_00] E, što manje žrtava,

3305
01:26:12,140 --> 01:26:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] to brzo i završiš priču.

3306
01:26:13,619 --> 01:26:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde da vas sad pitam.

3307
01:26:15,119 --> 01:26:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi kažu,

3308
01:26:15,880 --> 01:26:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] ista je agresija Rusije

3309
01:26:18,460 --> 01:26:19,720
[SPEAKER_01] na Ukrajinu

3310
01:26:19,720 --> 01:26:21,100
[SPEAKER_01] i Amerike i Izraela

3311
01:26:21,100 --> 01:26:21,600
[SPEAKER_01] na Iranu.

3312
01:26:21,600 --> 01:26:22,020
[SPEAKER_00] E, nije.

3313
01:26:22,020 --> 01:26:24,439
[SPEAKER_00] Izjednostavno grašenje

3314
01:26:24,439 --> 01:26:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] što dva rata ne postoje.

3315
01:26:25,880 --> 01:26:30,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoje dva rata.

3316
01:26:30,020 --> 01:26:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo lijepo objasnili

3317
01:26:32,079 --> 01:26:33,180
[SPEAKER_00] kako su ovi napravili

3318
01:26:33,180 --> 01:26:34,699
[SPEAKER_00] strategiju širenje NATO-a.

3319
01:26:34,699 --> 01:26:35,520
[SPEAKER_00] Neista da bi kolili

3320
01:26:35,520 --> 01:26:36,239
[SPEAKER_00] i doveli Rusiju

3321
01:26:36,239 --> 01:26:37,060
[SPEAKER_00] da mora ići u rat.

3322
01:26:37,060 --> 01:26:38,979
[SPEAKER_00] Isto su način.

3323
01:26:38,979 --> 01:26:40,979
[SPEAKER_00] Doveli Iran

3324
01:26:40,979 --> 01:26:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] da ga opkole

3325
01:26:41,680 --> 01:26:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] bazama

3326
01:26:42,159 --> 01:26:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ga mogli napasti.

3327
01:26:43,260 --> 01:26:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pa valjda bi bilo obrnuto

3328
01:26:46,859 --> 01:26:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovi Zapad

3329
01:26:48,579 --> 01:26:49,979
[SPEAKER_00] primijenio istu doktrinu,

3330
01:26:49,979 --> 01:26:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno istu,

3331
01:26:50,460 --> 01:26:50,899
[SPEAKER_00] pardon,

3332
01:26:50,899 --> 01:26:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] strategiju

3333
01:26:51,539 --> 01:26:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] kao što je primijenio

3334
01:26:52,319 --> 01:26:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] i ovdje.

3335
01:26:53,159 --> 01:26:54,479
[SPEAKER_01] obrnuto.

3336
01:26:54,479 --> 01:26:55,840
[SPEAKER_00] A ne obrnuto.

3337
01:26:55,840 --> 01:26:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to su se opet,

3338
01:26:57,159 --> 01:26:57,800
[SPEAKER_00] to sve,

3339
01:26:57,800 --> 01:26:59,560
[SPEAKER_00] onaj,

3340
01:26:59,560 --> 01:27:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] ovako,

3341
01:27:00,619 --> 01:27:01,779
[SPEAKER_00] to sam im govorio

3342
01:27:01,779 --> 01:27:02,380
[SPEAKER_00] istoj omisiji,

3343
01:27:02,380 --> 01:27:03,100
[SPEAKER_00] dva,

3344
01:27:03,100 --> 01:27:05,899
[SPEAKER_00] ista rata ne postoje.

3345
01:27:05,899 --> 01:27:07,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ne postoje.

3346
01:27:07,279 --> 01:27:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sve dobro su

3347
01:27:08,619 --> 01:27:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] usporeživali

3348
01:27:10,460 --> 01:27:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] ukrajinske rati

3349
01:27:12,319 --> 01:27:13,939
[SPEAKER_00] i solominski rati,

3350
01:27:13,939 --> 01:27:14,840
[SPEAKER_00] toko nema nikako veze.

3351
01:27:14,840 --> 01:27:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] E pa tako i ovo.

3352
01:27:16,420 --> 01:27:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje akteristi.

3353
01:27:18,779 --> 01:27:20,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ista je strategija.

3354
01:27:20,640 --> 01:27:23,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ista okultna oligarkija stoji.

3355
01:27:24,100 --> 01:27:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] a iza njih,

3356
01:27:24,640 --> 01:27:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] iznad njih iluminati.

3357
01:27:25,840 --> 01:27:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ista.

3358
01:27:26,180 --> 01:27:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ista je to ovdje.

3359
01:27:28,460 --> 01:27:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] Admirale,

3360
01:27:30,300 --> 01:27:31,520
[SPEAKER_01] hoćemo privest kraju.

3361
01:27:31,520 --> 01:27:32,819
[SPEAKER_01] Uf, šta je bilo ovi?

3362
01:27:32,819 --> 01:27:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] Gotovo sat i pol.

3363
01:27:33,920 --> 01:27:34,600
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to, evo,

3364
01:27:34,600 --> 01:27:35,640
[SPEAKER_00] idemo ovaj kraju.

3365
01:27:35,640 --> 01:27:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovako,

3366
01:27:36,859 --> 01:27:37,560
[SPEAKER_00] moje

3367
01:27:37,560 --> 01:27:39,819
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatske i Hrvati,

3368
01:27:39,819 --> 01:27:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] državne države Hrvatske.

3369
01:27:41,359 --> 01:27:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] U prošle emisije smo govorili,

3370
01:27:44,779 --> 01:27:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] i oni prošle emisije,

3371
01:27:45,760 --> 01:27:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] o unutarnju agresiju.

3372
01:27:46,920 --> 01:27:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] I mi imamo unutarnju agresiju.

3373
01:27:48,960 --> 01:27:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je naš identitet,

3374
01:27:51,239 --> 01:27:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] identitet Hrvatskih se napada,

3375
01:27:54,100 --> 01:27:56,140
[SPEAKER_00] a to da mi ne smemo reći da smo Hrvati,

3376
01:27:56,140 --> 01:27:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] ako kaže da se Hrvatom,

3377
01:27:57,340 --> 01:27:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] da se odmah ustaša.

3378
01:27:58,399 --> 01:28:00,239
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je ta iz okultna oligarkije.

3379
01:28:00,239 --> 01:28:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost,

3380
01:28:01,359 --> 01:28:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] takvih ima sljedbenika,

3381
01:28:02,960 --> 01:28:03,899
[SPEAKER_00] nerazumnih,

3382
01:28:03,899 --> 01:28:04,100
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

3383
01:28:04,100 --> 01:28:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] blagu riječ uporabiti,

3384
01:28:05,880 --> 01:28:07,640
[SPEAKER_00] sjede u Hrvatskom saboru

3385
01:28:07,640 --> 01:28:09,600
[SPEAKER_00] i mantraju svaki put isto mantrao

3386
01:28:09,600 --> 01:28:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] nekakvim ustašama i ostalo.

3387
01:28:11,119 --> 01:28:13,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ja idem cijelom Hrvatskom,

3388
01:28:13,060 --> 01:28:15,220
[SPEAKER_00] nisam susreo ni jednog jedinog ustaša.

3389
01:28:15,220 --> 01:28:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Nijednoga nisam susreo,

3390
01:28:17,340 --> 01:28:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] ni ustašcu,

3391
01:28:18,140 --> 01:28:19,399
[SPEAKER_00] nikoga nisam susreo,

3392
01:28:19,399 --> 01:28:21,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa bi ja volio kad budem,

3393
01:28:24,100 --> 01:28:24,939
[SPEAKER_00] porazgarao malo.

3394
01:28:24,939 --> 01:28:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se može prepoznati ustaša?

3395
01:28:26,500 --> 01:28:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja prvo mogu prepoznati,

3396
01:28:28,260 --> 01:28:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda,

3397
01:28:28,739 --> 01:28:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] budući da sam svima razgovarao

3398
01:28:30,859 --> 01:28:31,880
[SPEAKER_00] po Domarskom vratu,

3399
01:28:31,880 --> 01:28:33,680
[SPEAKER_00] u svim pregovora bio sa Srma,

3400
01:28:33,680 --> 01:28:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] sa svima mogu razgovarao,

3401
01:28:34,859 --> 01:28:36,399
[SPEAKER_00] pa bi ja razgovarao sa njim,

3402
01:28:36,399 --> 01:28:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] da idemo.

3403
01:28:36,800 --> 01:28:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne nametite hipoteku tamo gdje nema.

3404
01:28:39,500 --> 01:28:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ne dovodite nas u situaciju.

3405
01:28:42,279 --> 01:28:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kakva je to na rati

3406
01:28:44,000 --> 01:28:46,720
[SPEAKER_00] da ti zabranjuješ pjevanje?

3407
01:28:46,720 --> 01:28:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zarobljavnjivali su išli u zatvore

3408
01:28:49,819 --> 01:28:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] zbog vileva lebita u moje vremena,

3409
01:28:52,699 --> 01:28:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] a ja sam bio tada mlad,

3410
01:28:53,840 --> 01:28:56,479
[SPEAKER_00] ili ustani Bane i Jelačiću.

3411
01:28:56,479 --> 01:28:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] I sada ti pjevaš neku pjesmu,

3412
01:28:59,079 --> 01:29:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] u kontekstu neke pjesme,

3413
01:29:00,500 --> 01:29:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno riječi.

3414
01:29:01,539 --> 01:29:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] Govorili smo i za pojmu

3415
01:29:03,760 --> 01:29:04,600
[SPEAKER_00] dom sprem.

3416
01:29:04,600 --> 01:29:06,979
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda lijepo prozovite

3417
01:29:06,979 --> 01:29:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] i ovoga Seneku prozovite,

3418
01:29:12,560 --> 01:29:13,479
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on uporabio

3419
01:29:13,479 --> 01:29:16,239
[SPEAKER_00] Propatija Paramus.

3420
01:29:16,239 --> 01:29:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, za domovnu,

3421
01:29:17,859 --> 01:29:18,600
[SPEAKER_00] za dom sprem.

3422
01:29:18,600 --> 01:29:19,819
[SPEAKER_01] Možda je on bio prvi ustašan.

3423
01:29:19,819 --> 01:29:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] Možda je bio.

3424
01:29:20,899 --> 01:29:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ko znaš kod njih?

3425
01:29:21,840 --> 01:29:22,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, pardon, Cicerona.

3426
01:29:22,979 --> 01:29:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Cicerona, Cicerona.

3427
01:29:23,539 --> 01:29:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] Cicerona, govornik.

3428
01:29:24,500 --> 01:29:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] Cicerona.

3429
01:29:25,220 --> 01:29:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] E, hajde,

3430
01:29:26,300 --> 01:29:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] ostavite se toga.

3431
01:29:28,039 --> 01:29:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi živimo u pogmuljna vremena.

3432
01:29:30,000 --> 01:29:31,520
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte,

3433
01:29:31,520 --> 01:29:33,100
[SPEAKER_00] uništili se s ono što je bilo,

3434
01:29:33,100 --> 01:29:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] mi dobili rat sa spremnosti na žrtvu,

3435
01:29:35,260 --> 01:29:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] obranu.

3436
01:29:36,000 --> 01:29:37,100
[SPEAKER_00] A što oni rade?

3437
01:29:37,100 --> 01:29:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] Oni sada nama instaliraju.

3438
01:29:39,460 --> 01:29:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ove piličarnike gdje uništava hranu.

3439
01:29:43,699 --> 01:29:46,819
[SPEAKER_00] A to je ta druga mantra od Hernika Hizića,

3440
01:29:46,819 --> 01:29:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] ko kontrolira hranu, kontrolira državu.

3441
01:29:48,880 --> 01:29:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kontrolira ljude, da.

3442
01:29:49,140 --> 01:29:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mišljam u njegovog,

3443
01:29:50,760 --> 01:29:52,479
[SPEAKER_00] zašto vi ne razvijete novac?

3444
01:29:52,479 --> 01:29:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Date da sto više seljako biten

3445
01:29:55,539 --> 01:29:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] napravi tih pravi u prirode,

3446
01:29:58,220 --> 01:29:59,520
[SPEAKER_00] da žive kokoš i jaje,

3447
01:29:59,520 --> 01:30:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] da idemo i ćeš ti stvoriti diljem Hrvatske,

3448
01:30:02,079 --> 01:30:04,560
[SPEAKER_00] od otoka do naše Slavonije,

3449
01:30:04,560 --> 01:30:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] do Iloka,

3450
01:30:07,119 --> 01:30:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] i gore do Svjetog Martina na muri

3451
01:30:09,279 --> 01:30:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] i da ga umaga u Istri.

3452
01:30:13,220 --> 01:30:15,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pa tamo napravite ti svi da i obitelj ima,

3453
01:30:15,859 --> 01:30:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] a ne na jedno mjesto koje je ekološka mobba

3454
01:30:17,840 --> 01:30:18,659
[SPEAKER_00] i sve da napravlja.

3455
01:30:18,659 --> 01:30:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] Pa kako vi možete praviti u željavi

3456
01:30:22,260 --> 01:30:26,359
[SPEAKER_00] centar za prihvat ovih migranata?

3457
01:30:26,359 --> 01:30:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] I kako su vas ti evroopljeni

3458
01:30:28,640 --> 01:30:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] za koje se vi zakljetljene nasadili,

3459
01:30:30,560 --> 01:30:32,199
[SPEAKER_00] da bude malo grubliji?

3460
01:30:32,199 --> 01:30:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je registriran u prvoj zemlji?

3461
01:30:35,180 --> 01:30:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zato ste policičari glupli

3462
01:30:37,680 --> 01:30:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] pa nas zato stavili šengelski granicu

3463
01:30:40,000 --> 01:30:42,239
[SPEAKER_00] da oni mi registriramo prve teme migranta

3464
01:30:42,239 --> 01:30:43,840
[SPEAKER_00] a oni nama vrate nasad.

3465
01:30:43,840 --> 01:30:44,939
[SPEAKER_00] A što ste navratili?

3466
01:30:44,939 --> 01:30:48,140
[SPEAKER_00] Potencijalne se moguće

3467
01:30:48,140 --> 01:30:49,439
[SPEAKER_00] da ne govorim teroriste.

3468
01:30:49,439 --> 01:30:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je nama doveo i mijenja stanovništvo?

3469
01:30:52,539 --> 01:30:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] Pola milijuna ljudi, mladi, Istjera,

3470
01:30:55,600 --> 01:30:58,279
[SPEAKER_00] a dovede pola milijuna Hindusa.

3471
01:30:58,279 --> 01:31:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] Nepalaca sa Indije.

3472
01:31:00,779 --> 01:31:02,039
[SPEAKER_00] Indija je sad postala glavna.

3473
01:31:02,039 --> 01:31:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] Pa Indija je u rukama Velike Britanije.

3474
01:31:04,279 --> 01:31:06,779
[SPEAKER_00] Velika Britanija uvijek je bila protiv nas.

3475
01:31:06,779 --> 01:31:09,359
[SPEAKER_00] A ona je u mnogo čemu prevelila i Srba.

3476
01:31:09,359 --> 01:31:10,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je poruka i Srba.

3477
01:31:10,359 --> 01:31:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] I u Beogradu i u Zagrebu mi moramo doći s sebi.

3478
01:31:14,060 --> 01:31:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ćete ponovo ići i to da nas gurni

3479
01:31:16,880 --> 01:31:17,739
[SPEAKER_00] i ponovo neki rat.

3480
01:31:17,739 --> 01:31:18,600
[SPEAKER_00] Između nas.

3481
01:31:18,600 --> 01:31:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] Neće oni ratovati, nego će nas gurniti.

3482
01:31:21,779 --> 01:31:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome pamet u glavu i pustite, dakle, u Hrva pusti da ljudi govore.

3483
01:31:27,500 --> 01:31:30,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možete ove mantranje na hrvatskoj televiziji, to je užas, jedan.

3484
01:31:30,979 --> 01:31:36,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi koji ne znaju ništa, dakle, o vojnom umijeću, o ratovanju, o doktrinama, ne znaju ništa.

3485
01:31:36,939 --> 01:31:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Nikako vojci nisu bili.

3486
01:31:38,720 --> 01:31:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nikako oružje nisu ni sastavljali ni rastavljali.

3487
01:31:41,579 --> 01:31:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa od njemu ne znaju.

3488
01:31:42,579 --> 01:31:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] Nikakvu doktrinu ni svidljali, niči nisu zapovjedali.

3489
01:31:45,319 --> 01:31:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] I oni sada mantraju neprekidno.

3490
01:31:48,579 --> 01:31:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mora se čekati ovakva, kao ovakva emisija, Bogu hvala da je,

3491
01:31:53,880 --> 01:31:56,020
[SPEAKER_00] jer je rana vama svaka na čast.

3492
01:31:56,020 --> 01:31:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš zašto?

3493
01:31:56,539 --> 01:31:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] To ću ponavljati uvijek.

3494
01:31:58,079 --> 01:32:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi ljudi govore, pa kaže, admirale, gospođa Rijana, ona vas pusti, govorite.

3495
01:32:03,039 --> 01:32:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja kaže, je, ali ona i prati.

3496
01:32:04,579 --> 01:32:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ona zna stratešku razinu i uči, i Bogu hvala, a takvih nema na ovih medijima.

3497
01:32:11,579 --> 01:32:14,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovako, možemo mi svi izući iz ovoga.

3498
01:32:14,659 --> 01:32:18,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi smo marijanski narod, marijanski narod.

3499
01:32:18,220 --> 01:32:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, uvjera naš intet, čuvati obitelj i ne srljati glavu tamo,

3500
01:32:27,920 --> 01:32:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] ne stavljati glavu na giljotinu.

3501
01:32:29,840 --> 01:32:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jer on će pasiti na glavu, prije ili kasnije.

3502
01:32:33,619 --> 01:32:36,479
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, to je ona moja poruka što ima.

3503
01:32:36,479 --> 01:32:38,859
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo, da se ne palimo kao šim.

3504
01:32:38,859 --> 01:32:43,439
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nikakvo navijanje, ostavite navijanje za ihok.

3505
01:32:43,439 --> 01:32:46,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ostavite se navijanja, ostavite se toga.

3506
01:32:46,260 --> 01:32:49,319
[SPEAKER_00] Počnete razmišljati svojom glavom.

3507
01:32:49,319 --> 01:32:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek učili su mene, učim i ja sad.

3508
01:32:52,640 --> 01:32:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kui bono.

3509
01:32:54,260 --> 01:32:55,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kad vidiš nešto.

3510
01:32:55,600 --> 01:33:00,359
[SPEAKER_00] Samo, nisu latine, bihli tako da nisu tu sintagu našli.

3511
01:33:00,359 --> 01:33:01,640
[SPEAKER_00] Lisi tencu.

3512
01:33:02,279 --> 01:33:04,739
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kome koristi, kome šteti.

3513
01:33:04,739 --> 01:33:09,779
[SPEAKER_00] To pođište od toga i sam ćete, sa svojim zdravim razumom,

3514
01:33:09,779 --> 01:33:12,939
[SPEAKER_00] to je najveći božiji dar čovjeku, razum,

3515
01:33:12,939 --> 01:33:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne da ide proti Boga, nego da spozna veličinu Božjega dijela,

3516
01:33:16,180 --> 01:33:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] ćete doći do odgovora.

3517
01:33:18,180 --> 01:33:19,939
[SPEAKER_00] Kome koristi, kome šteti.

3518
01:33:19,939 --> 01:33:21,060
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki događaj koji ima.

3519
01:33:21,060 --> 01:33:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je moja poruka.

3520
01:33:22,760 --> 01:33:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam, admirale.

3521
01:33:24,079 --> 01:33:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] Molim, hvala i vama.

3522
01:33:25,199 --> 01:33:26,439
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam što za dodati.

3523
01:33:26,439 --> 01:33:29,600
[SPEAKER_01] Admiral Davor Domazet Lošo bio je gostu u ovom podcastu Mrežnica.

3524
01:33:29,600 --> 01:33:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] Vidimo se vrlo brzo.

3525
01:33:32,279 --> 01:33:36,020
[UNKNOWN] Hvala na sviđanju.

